name: TimeCoin (TIM)
description:
TimeCoin is the token based on the number of seconds in 100 years.  Time knows no boundaries of language or culture.  If you can tell time, you understand TimeCoin.  Based on the number of seconds in 100 years, 3,155,760,000 for 3 reasons...
1: To account for leap years.
2. To make amount owned easy to understand.  If you own 1%, you own 1 year of TimeCoin.
3. Denominations like cash.  Time breaks down into years, days, minutes, and seconds.
  Time is Universal. Time is Eternal.  Time is Money.
